Current exhibition: The winner took it all

Inspired by My Life Is Better Than Yours consciousness, where there's no future, only HERE and NOW.
Inspired by the consciousness of the people who run my country. 
5.Abril 2021 'till...


Previous installation: Survival shelter

Inspired by an article from 
Douglas Rushkoff,"Survival of the Richest"
https://onezero.medium.com/survival-of-the-richest-9ef6cddd0cc1
Of course, I made this installation with a dose of humor and optimism!
